html
  head
  body(style="background-color: #eef0f4; text-align: center; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; color: #47494d;")
    table(style="width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: collapse")
      tr
        td(style="height: 44px;")
          p(style='font-size: 10px; text-align: left; float: left')
            | Prizm Insight
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; border-bottom: 1px solid #dde3f1")
        td
          div(style='width: 100%; text-align: left')
            img(src="http://www.prizmapp.com/images/logo.png"
                alt="Prizm"
                style="margin: 12px 0px 12px 24px; height: 48px; width: 116px;")
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; border-bottom: 1px solid #dde3f1")
        td(style="height: 174px; vertical-align: middle, width: 100%; text-align: center; color: #25689a")
          p(style="font-size: 26px; color: #25689a;")
            | Hi #{ target.first_name },
          p(style="font-size: 26px; color: #25689a;")
            | We think you'll like this Insight
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; text-align: left;")
        td(style='padding-top: 24px')
          table(style="width: 558px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: collapse")
            tr(style='background-color: #eef0f4;')
              td(style='padding-left: 12px; padding-top: 18px; padding-bottom: 18px;')
                img(src='#{creator.profile_photo_url}' style='width: 50px;'
                + 'height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid black;'
                + 'clear: both; float: left;')
                p(style='font-size: 15px; font-weight: light; margin: 16px 5px 5px 68px; color: #25689a; text-transform: uppercase;')
                  | #{creator.name}
            tr(style="background-color: #eef0f4; text-align: center;")
              td(style='padding: 0px')
                img(src='#{insight.file_path}' style='width: 558px; height: 558px; margin-top: -1px;')
            tr(style="background-color: #eef0f4; text-align: left;")
              td(style='height: 60px;')
                p(style='font-size: 18px; color: #25689a; margin-left: 16px')
                  each tag in insight.hash_tags
                    | ##{tag.replace(/(^\s+|\s+$)/g, '') + ' '} 
            tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; text-align: left;")
              td(style='padding-left: 26px; padding-right: 26px;')
                p(style='font-size: 24px; margin-top: 24px; font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: 100;')
                  | #{ insight.title} <br/>
                  a(href='#{insight.link}'
                    style='font-size: 20px; color: #25689a; text-decoration: none;')
                    | #{insight.link}
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; height: 80px")
        td(style='padding-top: 24px;')
          p(style='font-size: 14px; line-height: 4px;')
          a(href='')
            | On a Mobile Device?
          p(style='font-size: 14px; line-height: 4px;')
            | Checkout this Insight in Prizm
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; height: 80px")
        td(style='padding-top: 12px;')
          div(style='background-color: #25689a; width: 128px; height: 48px; margin: 0px auto;')
            p(style='padding: 14px 10px 10px;')
              a(href='prizmapp://'
                style='color: white; font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: 100; font-size: 20px; text-decoration: none;')
                | Open Prizm
      tr(style="background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #dde3f1;")
        td(style='text-align: center; padding: 20px;')
          p(style='font-size: 14px; color: #25689a;') FOLLOW PRIZM
          a(href='https://www.facebook.com/prizmapp'
            style='text-decoration: none')
            img(src='http://www.prizmapp.com/images/facebook.png'
style='height: 32px; width: 32px;'
alt='Facebook')
          a(href='https://www.twitter.com/beprizmatic'
            style='text-decoration: none; margin-left: 32px;')
            img(src='http://www.prizmapp.com/images/twitter.png'
              style='height: 32px; width: 32px;'
              alt='Twitter')
          a(href='https://www.instagram.com/beprizmatic'
            style='text-decoration: none; margin-left: 32px;')
            img(src='http://www.prizmapp.com/images/instagram.png'
              style='height: 32px; width: 32px;'
              alt='Instagram')
      tr(style='background-color: #ffffff; border-top: 1px solid #dde3f1; text-align: center')
        td
          p(style="font-size: 10px; color: #25689a; padding: 12px 24px 0px 24px;")
            | You have received this email because you signed up for an account
            | on Prizm with the email address: 
            a(href='mailto:#{target.email}' 
              style="color: #25689a; text-decoration: none")
              | #{target.email}. 
            | We respect your privacy and hope that you enjoy these messages. 
            | If you would no longer like to  receive these emails, you can 
            | safely and easily unsubscribe below.
          p(style='color: #25689a; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px 0px 12px;')
            a(href='http://admin.prizmapp.com/unsubscribe/#{target.email}' 
              style='color: #25689a; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10px;') Unsubscribe 
            | |
            a(href='http://www.prizmapp.com/privacy' 
              style='color: #25689a; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10px;') 
              | Privacy Policy
      tr(style='text-align: left;')
        td
          p(style='font-size: 10px; padding: 10px 0px;')
            | Copyright &copy; 2014 Higher Altitude, Inc. All rights reserved.
